text: Eteke kono eta janapadabasi kiya enekuraa nahaâ€™la yisakale imana anile haya arau sihamtara imana sihamtara upakarata ahilehemtena? Kintu i'unuchara sampradayara bahirae, sihamte yetiya imana anile tetiya ami sihamtara paraa parthira jiranara lanchanamulaka sasti dura karailo arau sihamtaka kichu samayara babe jiranopabhoga karaibalai dilo
